#: instructor-training/_episodes/21-carpentries.md:57
msgid ""
"## Similarities and Differences between The Carpentries Lesson Programs"
msgstr ""

#: instructor-training/_episodes/21-carpentries.md:59
msgid ""
"All lesson programs under The Carpentries share the same value\n"
"of promoting efficient, shareable, and reproducible research practices.\n"
"Their aligned missions are accomplished by running accessible, inclusive training workshops; teaching openly available, high-quality, community-developed lessons; and fostering an active, inclusive, diverse instructor community that promotes and models reproducible research as a community norm."
msgstr ""

#: instructor-training/_episodes/21-carpentries.md:63
msgid ""
"Similarities between Software, Data and Library Carpentry workshops include:\n"
"*   a focus on technical skills.\n"
"*   an two-day format taught by volunteer instructors.\n"
"*   a focus on filling gaps in current training for learners."
msgstr ""

#: instructor-training/_episodes/21-carpentries.md:68
msgid ""
"The major differences between Software, Data and Library Carpentry workshops\n"
"are their content and intended audience."
