#: instructor-training/_episodes/21-carpentries.md:99
msgid "### Using the Names and Logos"
msgstr ""

#: instructor-training/_episodes/21-carpentries.md:101
msgid ""
"The names \"Software Carpentry\", \"Data Carpentry\" and \"Library Carpentry\"\n"
"and their respective logos\n"
"are all trademarked.\n"
"You may only call a workshop a Software Carpentry, Data Carpentry, or Library Carpentry workshop if:"
msgstr ""

# unordered list
#: instructor-training/_episodes/21-carpentries.md:106
msgid "*   it covers the core topics (see below),"
msgstr ""

# unordered list
#: instructor-training/_episodes/21-carpentries.md:107
msgid ""
"*   at least one of the instructors is a certified Carpentries Instructor,"
msgstr ""

# unordered list
#: instructor-training/_episodes/21-carpentries.md:108
msgid ""
